    <title>Top 10 Movies</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="./img/favicon.ico">
    <style>
        #links-items:hover {
            color: red;
        }

        .content {
            overflow: auto;
            position: relative;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color:aqua;">
    <div class="content" style="">
        <div class="container" style="padding-top:50px;">
            <div class="row" style="padding-top:50px;">
                <div class="col col-md-12" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-word; ">
                    If you don't like a movie in the dataset and you can't stand the name of it then just hit DELETE button<br />
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container" style=" padding-top: 50px;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-md-12">
                    <form method="Post" asp-action="moviedelete">
                        <input asp-for="id" hidden />
                        <label asp-for="title">Movie Title</label>
                        <input asp-for="title" class="form-control" disabled />
                        <br />
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Delete</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
